			<h2><a href="/blog/monday-elevate-ai-data-keynote/">Unlocking your data with AI: Insights from Monday.com Elevate</a></h2>
			<h3><span title="London, United Kingdom">ExCel, London</span> | Published <time>19 September 2024</time> in <a href="/categories/ai">AI</a> and <a href="/categories/data">Data</a> | 10 minute read | <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Unlocking%20your%20data%20with%20AI%3a%20Insights%20from%20Monday.com%20Elevate&url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fmonday-elevate-ai-data-keynote%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/twitter-x.svg" alt="Share this post on X" title="Share this post on X" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fmonday-elevate-ai-data-keynote%2f&xdOrigin=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f&xd_origin_host=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/linkedin.svg" alt="Share this post on LinkedIn" title="Share this post on LinkedIn" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Have a read&body=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fmonday-elevate-ai-data-keynote%2f"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/envelope.svg" alt="Share this post by Email" title="Share this post by Email" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://mariothomas.com/blog/monday-elevate-ai-data-keynote/" onclick="copyURL('copyit'); return false;" id="copyit"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Copy the Permalink to this post" title="Copy the Permalink to this post" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		<img src="/blog/monday-elevate-ai-data-keynote/img/mario-thomas-on-stage-elevate-monda-use-cases.png" title ="Mario Thomas on stage at Monday.com Elevate at ExCel London with a list of AI use cases on screen" alt="Mario Thomas on stage at Monday.com Elevate at ExCel London with a list of AI use cases on screen" width="735" height="490" style="float: left; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px">
		
		<p>Last week, I had the privilege of delivering a keynote presentation at Monday.com&rsquo;s Elevate conference in London. The topic, &ldquo;Leveraging data and artificial intelligence (AI) for organisational transformation,&rdquo; allowed me to challenge some common misconceptions about AI adoption and share practical insights on harnessing the power of existing data. In this post, I outline the key themes discussed and provide some additional context.</p>
		
