			<h2><a href="/blog/dawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week/">Dawn of the three-hour work week: AI&#39;s impact on employment and compensation</a></h2>
			<h3><span title="Vienna, Austria">Vienna</span> | Published <time>9 June 2024</time> in <a href="/categories/ai">AI</a> and <a href="/categories/board">Board</a> | 10 minute read | <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Dawn%20of%20the%20three-hour%20work%20week%3a%20AI%27s%20impact%20on%20employment%20and%20compensation&url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fdawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/twitter-x.svg" alt="Share this post on X" title="Share this post on X" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fdawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week%2f&xdOrigin=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f&xd_origin_host=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/linkedin.svg" alt="Share this post on LinkedIn" title="Share this post on LinkedIn" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Have a read&body=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fdawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week%2f"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/envelope.svg" alt="Share this post by Email" title="Share this post by Email" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://mariothomas.com/blog/dawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week/" onclick="copyURL('copyit'); return false;" id="copyit"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Copy the Permalink to this post" title="Copy the Permalink to this post" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		<img src="/blog/dawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week/img/dawn-of-the-three-hour-work-week.png" title ="A futuristic office seamlessly blended with a beach setting. It shows humans relaxing and working alongside AI robots, reflecting a balanced lifestyle where work and leisure coexist harmoniously (Image generated by ChatGPT 4o)." alt="A futuristic office seamlessly blended with a beach setting. It shows humans relaxing and working alongside AI robots, reflecting a balanced lifestyle where work and leisure coexist harmoniously (Image generated by ChatGPT 4o)." width="735" height="420" style="float: left; padding-right: 20px; padding-bottom: 20px">
		
		<p>As artificial intelligence (AI) advances into the workplace rapidly, one of the most pressing questions on everyone&rsquo;s mind is, &ldquo;If machines can do our jobs faster, more accurately, and at a lower cost, what happens to us?&rdquo; It&rsquo;s true that AI is beginning to redefine the very essence of work, raising concerns about the potential displacement of knowledge workers. However, I&rsquo;d like to propose an alternative perspective—one where those same workers earn the same or more whilst working far fewer hours.</p>
		
