			<h3><span title="London, United Kingdom">London</span> | Published <time>23 April 2024</time> in <a href="/categories/ai">AI</a> | 10 minute read | <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Amazon%20Bedrock%20launches%20Custom%20Model%20Import&url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fbedrock-custom-model-import%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/twitter-x.svg" alt="Share this post on X" title="Share this post on X" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fbedrock-custom-model-import%2f&xdOrigin=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f&xd_origin_host=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/linkedin.svg" alt="Share this post on LinkedIn" title="Share this post on LinkedIn" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Have a read&body=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fbedrock-custom-model-import%2f"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/envelope.svg" alt="Share this post by Email" title="Share this post by Email" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://mariothomas.com/blog/bedrock-custom-model-import/" onclick="copyURL('copyit'); return false;" id="copyit"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Copy the Permalink to this post" title="Copy the Permalink to this post" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/machine-learning/new-capabilities-make-it-easier-to-use-amazon-bedrock-to-build-and-scale-generative-ai-applications-and-deliver-impact" target="_blank" title="Read the AWS blog post about this here"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/box-arrow-up-right.svg" alt="London, United Kingdom" /></a></h3>
